com.yantra.yfc.rcp.wizard

Class YRCWizardEntity

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yantra.yfc.rcp.wizard.YRCWizardEntity
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IYRCWizardEntity
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    YRCWizardChildWizardHolder, YRCWizardPageHolder, YRCWizardRuleHolder

    public class YRCWizardEntity
extends java.lang.Object
implements IYRCWizardEntity
    Super class for all Wizard Entities. Entities currently constitute Pages and Rules. Any new entity type may subclass this and with a suitable model definition can fit into the existing scheme of things within the wizard.
    Author:
    vviswanathan
